name: Beastmaster Strikeforce - Double Ocho
description:
Beastmaster Collection Season 1

Double Ocho brings down the hammer wherever he goes. He does not tread lightly, exudes strength, and is a beast of little words. He will bring the fight to you and his rhino horn is imbued with earth rune magic. His ancestral hammer from his tribal home planet is imbued with lightning rune magic. Many are wise to not stand in Double Ocho's way.
